    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>An instance of this structure should be used by the adaptor to send a multi-point event to <ref refid="namespaceDali" kindref="compound">Dali</ref> core.</para>
<para>This class can contain one or multiple touch points. It also contains the time at which the event occurred. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
